<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="32" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="32">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="32">Colonies hyaline. Mycelium superficial on the 3% OA. Colony margin smooth. Colonies on 2% MEA flat, reaching 85 mm diam in 10 d at 25 °C. No growth observed at 5 and 35 °C. Optimal temperature for growth 25 °C.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
